{"tid":329960,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N個 生活中會令心情變差既小事/時刻","createTime":"2017-07-20T19:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T17:09:24.000Z","uid":25496,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"c446f63ac78f833664f788b9360813c3a8a37b48","tid":329960,"uid":25496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:04:02.000Z","msg":"我諗唔算強迫症掛 但呢啲小事真係會令人燥底 或者影響到個日心情...<br />\n<br />\n窗邊一撻撻既頭油<br />\n真係好撚想講呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身坐巴士好鐘意坐窗邊 但總有啲仆街好撚乞人憎 會貼個頭留玻璃度 咁就成撻油係玻璃度 睇落唔爽之餘 阻撚住睇景<br />\n<br />\n落雨著波鞋 幾小心都好 鞋身入水<br />\n<br />\n返工就黎遲到個時 狗鐵延誤<br />\n<br />\n出左門好先發現唔記得帶鎖匙<br />\n<br />\n盒裝野飲插飲管 唔小心成枝隊左落去<br />\n<br />\n嗌完野飲先醒起唔記得叫無糖/走冰etc.<br />\n<br />\n譚仔姨姨幫曬全部人落單 唯獨睇唔到自己<br />\n<br />\n趕頭趕命咁跑去巴士站個時 見到要搭個架車係面前 徐徐咁開走左<br />\n<br />\n食subway個時this this this完 俾錯野我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗到再補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c737ff0ba983df369c33dc8942da2d3c1e9174","tid":329960,"uid":121397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:12:40.000Z","msg":"送車尾<br />\n買野無自己個size <br />\n男朋友唔應機"},{"pid":"591a797ed11e5099b10974a7a4198f84b4599165","tid":329960,"uid":77516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:13:36.000Z","msg":"一起身個頭feel到油油地<br />\n朝早冇買咖啡"},{"pid":"7e411b19407c5b89747712cc2165052f53ef7129","tid":329960,"uid":49250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:14:26.000Z","msg":"唔夠訓 <br />\n返工受氣 <br />\n比廢老阻住"},{"pid":"9bea89ded4c63c0fb3817883098b1b4905eeb68d","tid":329960,"uid":25496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:20:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>送車尾<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">買野無自己個size </span><br />\n男朋友唔應機</blockquote><br />\n好撚中 屌揀完一大輪無自己碼